    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动作爽斗，博弈新秀</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >肉搏爆发激斗厮杀，射击迸发激烈火花。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动作为根，竞技为魂；各式博弈，造就专属于《战栗绝境》的战斗深度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战，就不屈不挠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246460/extras/02354af3d7a7cff39ed9cdb3bb5e1125.poster.avif?t=1765335390\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246460/extras/02354af3d7a7cff39ed9cdb3bb5e1125.webm?t=1765335390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精准反击，痛快终结</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >反击一刻，逢凶化吉；终结一发，化险为夷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独创反击系统上演精彩镜头，独特终结画面激活痛快体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >决，就不遗余力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246460/extras/6d9f635abf52be3ad16a97b4b627fb78.poster.avif?t=1765335390\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246460/extras/6d9f635abf52be3ad16a97b4b627fb78.webm?t=1765335390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>生物机甲，浴血奋战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >浩劫之余，舍命一搏；绝望之际，异军突起。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在浩劫肆虐的世界中成为身着生物机甲的“异军”，在光怪陆离的战场上创造属于你的进化之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >异，就不拘一格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246460/extras/2ed1fdf1c0a2b1d417dae28a0a0d0621.poster.avif?t=1765335390\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246460/extras/2ed1fdf1c0a2b1d417dae28a0a0d0621.webm?t=1765335390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多面角色，多变决策</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >十二异员，各负使命；百余天赋，各有妙招。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论个体之争还是团体之战，都将在梦境战场中上演精彩的斗争，在激烈战斗中解锁更强的天赋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >变，就不要设限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246460/extras/5d8ae0ae629066a61d3c9b39396b54f9.poster.avif?t=1765335390\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246460/extras/5d8ae0ae629066a61d3c9b39396b54f9.webm?t=1765335390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>模式革新，战备常青</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运营、团战、单挑，各图各派，一款全有。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快斗、哨塔攻防、单挑……不同模式，不同体验；不同装备，不同战术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新，就不落俗套。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246460/extras/4d61a9139e2aa52d9c18aaa254e3d1bf.poster.avif?t=1765335390\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246460/extras/4d61a9139e2aa52d9c18aaa254e3d1bf.webm?t=1765335390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们致力于打造一个充满激情与挑战的游戏世界，期待您的加入，共同见证《战栗绝境》的成长与蜕变。您的每一次反馈和建议，都是我们前进的动力，让我们在这场冒险中，共同创造属于我们的传奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>当前版本仍处于开发阶段，部分内容和功能还在调优中，不代表游戏最终品质，请以最终上线版本为准。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【关注我们】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ群：727707831</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获取《战栗绝境》的最新动态和消息，请在Steam平台加入愿望单，并关注我们的媒体平台账号。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们诚挚邀请每一位玩家在Steam平台将《战栗绝境》加入愿望单，以表达您对游戏的支持和期待。您的每一次关注和支持都是我们不断前进的动力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
